text: Alyssa Gialamas (born 5 December 1995) is an American Paralympic swimmer who competes in backstroke and freestyle swimming events in international level events. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Baltimore Category:Sportspeople from Cranston, Rhode Island Category:Paralympic swimmers of the United States Category:Swimmers at the 2012 Summer Paralympics Category:Swimmers at the 2016 Summer Paralympics Category:Medalists at the World Para Swimming Championships
